summary: I’m watching the last Google Feud again because procrastination (and why doesn’t it have a million views yet??) and it’s such a...
body:
I’m watching the last Google Feud again because procrastination (and why doesn’t it have a million views yet??) and it’s such a great video but jfc they were so exhausted, it looked like they were drunk.

Dan couldn’t think of what to comment so he just repeated what he read in an accent and Phil kept giving us unrestrained Love Eyes Lester, which I enjoy a lot actually so that was fun. 

My question is: why is Phil’s go-to forfeit to lick something? Do they dare each other to lick things all the time? Dan dared Phil to eat a piece of raw pumpkin in the carving pumpkin vid and Phil first assumed he was meant to lick it and then proposed to lick it as a counter-offer like that makes any sense?? What goes on in the Lester-Howell household??
